I'd love to go further, but have spent all day on this, so want to get the MVP up. Once I get my Ubuntu machine and I'm not in the way anymore, you guys can have all the fun you want!

So, I guess now you just need to give me the command with verification code and then I save the files you generated in the designated folder, update the prompt with the verification, push to git and I'm all set to transition right?
